\

\b Installation
\b0 \
\
Install 
\i ofxSyphon
\i0  in the 
\i addons
\i0  folder of your openFrameworks installation.\
Install the sample project 
\i SyphonExample
\i0  into the 
\i apps/addonExamples
\i0  folder of your openFrameworks installation.\
   \

\b Instructions
\b0 \
\
To add ofxSyphon to your project, you need to drag the 
\i ofxSyphon
\i0  addon folder into your project (like any other OF add-on). Consult 
\i SyphonExample
\i0  to see how ofxSyphon works.\
